{"tid":2259481,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國最高法院否決威斯康星州點算大選日後收到的郵遞選票","createTime":"2020-10-27T00:42:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T03:54:15.000Z","uid":295230,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5d6b746fe820bb5b12451c364354369f8444fe51","tid":2259481,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T00:42:49.000Z","msg":"美國最高法院推翻地方法院裁決，不容許威斯康星州點算在11月3日大選投票日後收到的郵遞選票。聯邦地方法院早前裁定，只要郵件蓋上投票日前的郵戳，在投票日後6日內送到的威斯康星州選票都算有效。 共和黨一直反對延長點票期限，認為選民有充足時間在投票日前遞交選票，不應臨近大選才改變規則。不過民主黨就指，因應大量選民以郵遞方式投票，加上疫情等挑戰，必須延長點算選票的期限。"},{"pid":"4b0cd0084702a6709fcbf6e5741769d2d4bd61ac","tid":2259481,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T00:42:54.000Z","msg":"原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2363347\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2363347&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETf3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=e874b305\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2363347</a>"},{"pid":"35ed9748c86e134ff4445a9fe7dbcc895ea5696e","tid":2259481,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T00:46:36.000Z","msg":"可惜賓洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690747bb44bce5b8c87c9cc490ba3c10531f5ae7","tid":2259481,"uid":195164,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"35ed9748c86e134ff4445a9fe7dbcc895ea5696e","tid":2259481,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T00:46:36.000Z","msg":"可惜賓洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:40:33.000Z","msg":"當時最高法院未齊腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo